-- MOVES-Matthieu Ressencourt joins BCS Financial as managing director
-- 
-- Wed Jul 23, 2014 05:57AM EDT
-- None



July 23 (Reuters) - Russian brokerage BCS Financial Group said it appointed Matthieu Ressencourt as managing director and head of equity derivatives trading in London.

In his new role, Ressencourt will report to Joseph Dayan, managing director of BCS Financial Group in London, the company said.